tmjmenu (2.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * REWRITE COMPLETA EM RUST. TMJMenu+TMJDock agora sao Rust + gtk4-rs
    + libadwaita (era Python + PyGObject).
  * 2 binarios: /usr/bin/tmjmenu (popup search) + /usr/bin/tmjdock (dock).
  * Architecture: amd64. Build via cargo no CI.
  * Modulos shared: monitors.rs, config.rs, search.rs, launcher.rs,
    widgets.rs, x11.rs.
  * TMJMenu popup UI com SearchEntry + ListBox, fuzzy filter, keyboard nav.
  * TMJDock com gtk4-layer-shell (Wayland) + X11 fallback.

 -- TMJOs Team <tmjos-archive@tmjsistemas.com.br>  Fri, 06 Jun 2026 12:00:00 -0300
